asteroids.model

Class Bullet

  • java.lang.Object
    • asteroids.model.Entity
      • asteroids.model.Bullet

  • public class Bullet
extends Entity
    A class of bullets, which are entities, involving a ship, a source ship and a collision counter.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Simon Merckx and Tobias Cornille. We both study informatics (1ba). Private repo on https://github.com/tobiascornille/Asteroids Please send us an email with your account info so we can add you as a contributer.
    Invariants:
  • The ship of each bullet must be a valid ship for any bullet.
        isValidShip(getShip())
  • The source ship of each bullet must be a valid source ship for this bullet.
        isValidSourceShip(getSourceShip())
  • The collision counter of each bullet must be a valid collision counter for any bullet.
        isValidCollisionCounter(getCollisionCounter())
